Name: dobyemail
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Do By Email is a comprehensive Python package for handling various email operations. It provides a set of utilities and classes to simplify email-related tasks in your Python projects.
Home-page: https://github.com/dobyemail/python
Author: Tom Sapletta
Author-email: info@softreck.dev
